snippet.title: WE BEAT THE BOSS!
snippet.description:
Metamon is a Free-To-Play PvX Monster Hunter game and universe where you build your career by hunting for rare and powerful monsters and compete against others for supremacy!

Play our Open Beta today: http://metamon.gg
